    "en": {
      "title": "Crisis resolved within 5 months: Central Bank Governor",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Central Bank Governor Nandalal Weerasinghe has said that the solution to the economic crisis in Sri Lanka can be found within the next 5 months.",
        "He said that Sri Lanka has a clear plan and a clear path, and by following it, Sri Lanka's current economic crisis can be resolved in the next 5 months.",
        "Therefore, Central Bank Governor Nandalal Weerasinghe said that people should act with patience. (a)"
      ],
